&lt;h1 id="1-base64-copy-paste-linux-to-windows">&lt;strong>1. Base64 Copy Paste (Linux to Windows)&lt;/strong>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h3 id="linux---encode-the-file-to-base64">Linux - Encode the file to Base64&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cat file &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> base64 -w 0&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nv">aGFjay5jb20uY3kgYXQgeW91ciBzZXJ2aWNlICg6Cg&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Copy the output and paste it to a PowerShell function for decoding&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h3 id="windows---decoding-base64-string">Windows - Decoding Base64 string&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c" data-lang="c">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">IO&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">File&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">WriteAllBytes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;C:\Users\Public&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">\f&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">ile&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Convert&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">FromBase64String&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;aGFjay5jb20uY3kgYXQgeW91ciBzZXJ2aWNlICg6Cg==&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">cat&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nl">C&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">\&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Users&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">\&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Public&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">\&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>